channel.title: Problems with VPS/DNS hosting
channel.description: Hi, yesterday i purchased the buisness plan from vpsland at 34$ a month. now the problem i have is, after i connected to the vps, downloaded no-ip, my server files, and Java JDK 6 update 14 and ran my server i tryed to login via no-ip ipaddress and my vps's ip and both told me the server was offline. but i was looking at my run.bat file after i left it open for 3hrs and it shows that some user got logged in and tryed a few commands then logged out after a while. but im yet or any one i ask to try is yet to login. please help [br][br][size=1]Posted on: July 21, 2009, 03:36:07 pm[/size][hr]any one know anything on this subject? haha
